# SafeHEIC

Offline HEIC to JPG converter for Windows.

<img src="assets/screenshot.png" width="720">

## Features

- Offline conversion
- No upload
- Drag & drop support
- Folder conversion
- English / Japanese UI
- Open source

## Why SafeHEIC?

Many HEIC converters require uploading photos to external servers.

SafeHEIC converts files locally on your Windows PC.

Your images never leave your machine.

## Download

Download the latest version from GitHub Releases.

## Usage

1. Drag & drop HEIC files or folders
2. JPG files are created automatically
3. No internet connection required

## Mac users

macOS already supports HEIC files natively.

SafeHEIC is mainly intended for Windows users who need a simple offline converter.

## Open source

Source code is available on GitHub.

## Support development

If this tool helped you, consider supporting development.

